Original: Welcome bac--oh, my! I think this is
our first meeting, actually. Are you
new explorers?
[Page]
Welcome to the Saehrimnir Inn. Lots
of our explorers use this place as
a base between excursions.
[Page]
If you get hurt or tired, come back
here and get a good rest.
[Page]
We have a clinic in the back, too!
You're welcome to use it if you have
any ailments or wounds to treat.
Translation: Welcome bac--oh, my! I think this is
our first meeting, actually. Are you
new explorers?
[Page]
Welcome to the Saehrimnir Inn. Lots
of our explorers use this place as
a base between excursions.
[Page]
If you get hurt or tired, come back
here and get a good rest.
[Page]
We have a clinic in the back, too!
You're welcome to use it if you have
any ailments or wounds to treat.

Original: Oh! Welcome back, dearies. And thank
you so much for taking care of my
little grocery list.
[Page]
I promised you I'd set aside extra
storage space for the [Guild] Guild,
and that's just what I've done!
Translation: Oh! Welcome back, dearies. And thank
you so much for taking care of my
little grocery list.
[Page]
I promised you I'd set aside extra
storage space for the [Guild] Guild,
and that's just what I've done!

Original: [Color:3]Your storage space has been expanded.[Color:0]
Translation: [Color:3]Your storage space has been expanded.[Color:0]

Original: [Color:3]Your storage space has been expanded.[Color:0]
Translation: [Color:3]Your storage space has been expanded.[Color:0]

Original: [Color:3]Your storage space has been expanded.[Color:0]
Translation: [Color:3]Your storage space has been expanded.[Color:0]

Original: [Color:3]Your storage space has been expanded.[Color:0]
Translation: [Color:3]Your storage space has been expanded.[Color:0]

Original: And don't worry, dearies, it'll still
be free to use whenever you want!
Translation: And don't worry, dearies, it'll still
be free to use whenever you want!

Original: Goodness, I just realized how much
space you have. That skinny little
girl at the atelier could live in it.
[Page]
I don't think I can give you anymore,
but if I ever have any more requests,
I hope you'll take them anyway!
Translation: Goodness, I just realized how much
space you have. That skinny little
girl at the atelier could live in it.
[Page]
I don't think I can give you anymore,
but if I ever have any more requests,
I hope you'll take them anyway!

Original: You're the [Guild] Guild, right?
Oh, explorers have such lovely names
for their guilds.
[Page]
I think your guild name has a very
nice ring to it, dearies.
[Page]
What inspired the name [Guild],
if that's all right to ask?
Translation: You're the [Guild] Guild, right?
Oh, explorers have such lovely names
for their guilds.
[Page]
I think your guild name has a very
nice ring to it, dearies.
[Page]
What inspired the name [Guild],
if that's all right to ask?

Original: Welcome back, dearies. I see you've
finished that mission you got at the
Grand Court.
[Page]
Good for you! Now you can go out on
your skyship to gather food.
[Page]
Oh, but silly me. I should be cooking
you dinner to celebrate!
Translation: Welcome back, dearies. I see you've
finished that mission you got at the
Grand Court.
[Page]
Good for you! Now you can go out on
your skyship to gather food.
[Page]
Oh, but silly me. I should be cooking
you dinner to celebrate!

Original: Oh, welcome back. Are you having fun,
sailing all across the skies?
[Page]
The Windy Plains are famous for the
delicious veggies that grow there.
The [Item:2067]s and [Item:2068]s...
[Page]
Oh, but don't eat the [Item:2069]!
You'll get a stomachache!
Translation: Oh, welcome back. Are you having fun,
sailing all across the skies?
[Page]
The Windy Plains are famous for the
delicious veggies that grow there.
The [Item:2067]s and [Item:2068]s...
[Page]
Oh, but don't eat the [Item:2069]!
You'll get a stomachache!

Original: Most of the ingredients for the food
we serve are from the market near the
outskirts of the city.
[Page]
A good amount of what they sell there
was brought back by explorers!
[Page]
The food in tonight's dinner might
very well have been made with the
ingredients you gathered yesterday.
Translation: Most of the ingredients for the food
we serve are from the market near the
outskirts of the city.
[Page]
A good amount of what they sell there
was brought back by explorers!
[Page]
The food in tonight's dinner might
very well have been made with the
ingredients you gathered yesterday.

Original: There have been so many attacks by
that red bear! All those poor soldiers
and explorers coming to the clinic...
[Page]
You dearies be careful out there. If
something looks like trouble, don't
chase after it without thinking!
Translation: There have been so many attacks by
that red bear! All those poor soldiers
and explorers coming to the clinic...
[Page]
You dearies be careful out there. If
something looks like trouble, don't
chase after it without thinking!

Original: Let's hear it for my dear [Guild]
Guild! I heard you broke through
the northern barrier... Amazing!
[Page]
I think a celebration is in order.
We just got a fine ostrich, so I'll go
out back and wring its neck for you.
Translation: Let's hear it for my dear [Guild]
Guild! I heard you broke through
the northern barrier... Amazing!
[Page]
I think a celebration is in order.
We just got a fine ostrich, so I'll go
out back and wring its neck for you.

Original: Oh, welcome back. Say, have you
ever eaten something called a
Dragon Crystal?
[Page]
It's supposed to be picked off a
terrible dragon's body... That's why
it's so rarely found on the market.
[Page]
But if it was me... I'd rather cook
the actual dragon meat than whatever
these crystals it leaves behind are.
[Page]
See here, this butcher's knife? I had
the master of the atelier make it for
me! It's so nice and sharp.
Translation: Oh, welcome back. Say, have you
ever eaten something called a
Dragon Crystal?
[Page]
It's supposed to be picked off a
terrible dragon's body... That's why
it's so rarely found on the market.
[Page]
But if it was me... I'd rather cook
the actual dragon meat than whatever
these crystals it leaves behind are.
[Page]
See here, this butcher's knife? I had
the master of the atelier make it for
me! It's so nice and sharp.

Original: Oh, welcome back! And did you finally
find a new labyrinth to explore,
hmmm?
[Page]
In that case, I'll cook a special
feast tonight! All that good food
will go to your success.
[Page]
Oh, did I ever tell you that the
Outland Count sometimes comes in
for a bite in our dining hall?
[Page]
The way he oohs and aaahs over his
food makes me so happy to have him
sample my cooking.
Translation: Oh, welcome back! And did you finally
find a new labyrinth to explore,
hmmm?
[Page]
In that case, I'll cook a special
feast tonight! All that good food
will go to your success.
[Page]
Oh, did I ever tell you that the
Outland Count sometimes comes in
for a bite in our dining hall?
[Page]
The way he oohs and aaahs over his
food makes me so happy to have him
sample my cooking.

Original: So they tell me you've met some funny-
looking people called Vessels.
[Page]
Some of the other explorers said they
have six arms and eight legs! They
sound horrible...
[Page]
Although... hmm...
[Page]
I wonder what kind of food they like.
Translation: So they tell me you've met some funny-
looking people called Vessels.
[Page]
Some of the other explorers said they
have six arms and eight legs! They
sound horrible...
[Page]
Although... hmm...
[Page]
I wonder what kind of food they like.

Original: Oh, my! Welcome back, dearies. They
tell me the new land you found is
awfully cold.
[Page]
Something told me you'd be freezing,
so I prepared some hot soup.
[Page]
Come by the dining hall as soon as
you're ready!
Translation: Oh, my! Welcome back, dearies. They
tell me the new land you found is
awfully cold.
[Page]
Something told me you'd be freezing,
so I prepared some hot soup.
[Page]
Come by the dining hall as soon as
you're ready!

Original: We've had a lot of Vessels as guests
here lately! The more, the merrier,
that's what I say.
[Page]
Tonight's dinner is a special dish I
came up with to suit the Vessels'
taste.
[Page]
It's health food made with fruits and
herbs from the Misty Ravine. I hope
you like it!
Translation: We've had a lot of Vessels as guests
here lately! The more, the merrier,
that's what I say.
[Page]
Tonight's dinner is a special dish I
came up with to suit the Vessels'
taste.
[Page]
It's health food made with fruits and
herbs from the Misty Ravine. I hope
you like it!

Original: Oh, hello, dearies. Maybe you can
explain something about the explorers
making trips to the Golden Lair...
[Page]
When I see them off, they're bundled
up warm, but when they come back again
they're wearing next to nothing!
[Page]
Wh-What kind of place have you dearies
been going to!?
Translation: Oh, hello, dearies. Maybe you can
explain something about the explorers
making trips to the Golden Lair...
[Page]
When I see them off, they're bundled
up warm, but when they come back again
they're wearing next to nothing!
[Page]
Wh-What kind of place have you dearies
been going to!?

Original: So I heard this time, you met some
folks called the Sentinels?
[Page]
Everyone's been buzzing over how
they're big enough to crush a skyship
in one hand! They must eat a lot.
[Page]
Hmm...
[Page]
I wonder if it's time to break out
that one dish...
Translation: So I heard this time, you met some
folks called the Sentinels?
[Page]
Everyone's been buzzing over how
they're big enough to crush a skyship
in one hand! They must eat a lot.
[Page]
Hmm...
[Page]
I wonder if it's time to break out
that one dish...

Original: Congratulations, dearies! It sounds
like you've broken new ground again.
[Page]
Lately, we've had humans, Vessels, and
Sentinels here at the Saehrimnir Inn.
It's like a big pot of stew...
[Page]
Stew! That would be just the thing
for dinner tonight. I hope you'll
be there!
Translation: Congratulations, dearies! It sounds
like you've broken new ground again.
[Page]
Lately, we've had humans, Vessels, and
Sentinels here at the Saehrimnir Inn.
It's like a big pot of stew...
[Page]
Stew! That would be just the thing
for dinner tonight. I hope you'll
be there!

Original: Oh, do you know, I haven't seen Whirl
or Wind lately. Do you know where they
might have gone?
[Page]
Huh...?
[Page]
W-Was he just one person? Goodness...
Who was I thinking of...?
Translation: Oh, do you know, I haven't seen Whirl
or Wind lately. Do you know where they
might have gone?
[Page]
Huh...?
[Page]
W-Was he just one person? Goodness...
Who was I thinking of...?

Original: Oh, my! Welcome back, dearies. What's
that now? You want to see my pot?
[Page]
I'm sorry, but maybe you should come
back some other time. She's not in
a very good mood right now...
[Page]
Hm? Me? Oh, no, I'm fine! The pot's
the one in the bad mood.
Translation: Oh, my! Welcome back, dearies. What's
that now? You want to see my pot?
[Page]
I'm sorry, but maybe you should come
back some other time. She's not in
a very good mood right now...
[Page]
Hm? Me? Oh, no, I'm fine! The pot's
the one in the bad mood.

Original: First the Vessels, then the Sentinels,
now these Imperials... I've been told
they look just like us.
[Page]
I wonder...
[Page]
I hope they don't throw their goblets
on the floor once they've finished
their drinks...
Translation: First the Vessels, then the Sentinels,
now these Imperials... I've been told
they look just like us.
[Page]
I wonder...
[Page]
I hope they don't throw their goblets
on the floor once they've finished
their drinks...

Original: Oh! Welcome back. Things have been so
busy ever since the Imperials started
showing up here.
[Page]
I've been so tired out that my
eyesight must be getting blurry.
It's hard to see Yggdrasil...
[Page]
It withered...? What are you talking
about, dearies?
Translation: Oh! Welcome back. Things have been so
busy ever since the Imperials started
showing up here.
[Page]
I've been so tired out that my
eyesight must be getting blurry.
It's hard to see Yggdrasil...
[Page]
It withered...? What are you talking
about, dearies?

Original: Did Yggdrasil really wither away?
I only believe what I can see with
my own eyes.
[Page]
Then again... if Yggdrasil was really
gone, I couldn't see it, could I...?
[Page]
I'm starting to confuse myself.
Do you believe that the hole in the
middle of a donut exists?
Translation: Did Yggdrasil really wither away?
I only believe what I can see with
my own eyes.
[Page]
Then again... if Yggdrasil was really
gone, I couldn't see it, could I...?
[Page]
I'm starting to confuse myself.
Do you believe that the hole in the
middle of a donut exists?

Original: Welcome back, dearies. Are any of
you hurt?
[Page]
The explorers who get carried in
here lately are in worse and worse
condition.
[Page]
I don't worry about you so much since
you're all so strong, but please be
careful anyway.
Translation: Welcome back, dearies. Are any of
you hurt?
[Page]
The explorers who get carried in
here lately are in worse and worse
condition.
[Page]
I don't worry about you so much since
you're all so strong, but please be
careful anyway.

Original: Oh! Welcome back, dearies. I'd say
your journey is nearing the end--does
that sound right?
[Page]
It's easy to tell by how hard you've
all been working.
[Page]
We have some delicious goat meat in,
so I'll cook something that'll raise
your spirits for the next outing!
Translation: Oh! Welcome back, dearies. I'd say
your journey is nearing the end--does
that sound right?
[Page]
It's easy to tell by how hard you've
all been working.
[Page]
We have some delicious goat meat in,
so I'll cook something that'll raise
your spirits for the next outing!

Original: All the explorers who come through
here are busy lately... Is something
going on?
[Page]
I haven't been sleeping much either.
It looks like Yggdrasil is swaying
back and forth, like it's walking...
[Page]
A Titan? What's this about?
Translation: All the explorers who come through
here are busy lately... Is something
going on?
[Page]
I haven't been sleeping much either.
It looks like Yggdrasil is swaying
back and forth, like it's walking...
[Page]
A Titan? What's this about?

Original: Well! It sounds like you all got
yourselves into a fine mess without
me ever realizing.
[Page]
But... your job is to have adventures,
and mine is to keep you fed with
delicious meals.
[Page]
I don't really need to know what
you're up to to do my part, do I? We
can go about our business as usual.
Translation: Well! It sounds like you all got
yourselves into a fine mess without
me ever realizing.
[Page]
But... your job is to have adventures,
and mine is to keep you fed with
delicious meals.
[Page]
I don't really need to know what
you're up to to do my part, do I? We
can go about our business as usual.

Original: You and I are the same as always,
but...
[Page]
Is it just me, or is Yggdrasil more
beautiful than usual today?
Translation: You and I are the same as always,
but...
[Page]
Is it just me, or is Yggdrasil more
beautiful than usual today?

Original: Hm? Those clothes... Are you going
back out to explore some more?
[Page]
But come on, what's left to do?
You already defeated the Titan and
conquered Yggdrasil.
[Page]
Where else would you go... Oh? You
found a new labyrinth?
[Page]
Goodness! Then I guess your days of
adventure really aren't over. I'll be
adventurous with tonight's meal, too!
Translation: Hm? Those clothes... Are you going
back out to explore some more?
[Page]
But come on, what's left to do?
You already defeated the Titan and
conquered Yggdrasil.
[Page]
Where else would you go... Oh? You
found a new labyrinth?
[Page]
Goodness! Then I guess your days of
adventure really aren't over. I'll be
adventurous with tonight's meal, too!

Original: Welcome to the Saehrimnir Inn! Tonight
we'll be serving Imperial-Style
Vegetable Stew, and... Hm?
[Page]
Oh! Welcome back, dearies. I'm sorry
I've been so busy...
[Page]
Since the Outland Count invited the
Imperials here, we've opened the inn
to them while their paperwork's done.
[Page]
I'm practicing cooking dishes that
those Imperial people will like.
[Page]
They seem nervous right now, poor
dears, but I think it won't be long
before they break out into smiles.
Translation: Welcome to the Saehrimnir Inn! Tonight
we'll be serving Imperial-Style
Vegetable Stew, and... Hm?
[Page]
Oh! Welcome back, dearies. I'm sorry
I've been so busy...
[Page]
Since the Outland Count invited the
Imperials here, we've opened the inn
to them while their paperwork's done.
[Page]
I'm practicing cooking dishes that
those Imperial people will like.
[Page]
They seem nervous right now, poor
dears, but I think it won't be long
before they break out into smiles.

Original: G-Goodness! Did I hear right that
you'll be leaving Tharsis once you've
explored this newest labyrinth?
[Page]
Oh my... I just thought that you'd
stay here in our city forever.
[Page]
What should I do? I haven't thought
yet what I might give you as a
farewell gift.
[Page]
Oh! I know! My pot!
[Page]
It might not seem like much, but
please take this pot with you as a
souvenir of your time in Tharsis.
[Page]
Ahahaha...
Translation: G-Goodness! Did I hear right that
you'll be leaving Tharsis once you've
explored this newest labyrinth?
[Page]
Oh my... I just thought that you'd
stay here in our city forever.
[Page]
What should I do? I haven't thought
yet what I might give you as a
farewell gift.
[Page]
Oh! I know! My pot!
[Page]
It might not seem like much, but
please take this pot with you as a
souvenir of your time in Tharsis.
[Page]
Ahahaha...

Original: As you enter the inn, you see the
innkeeper in the hall, chatting with
an unfamiliar face.
Translation: As you enter the inn, you see the
innkeeper in the hall, chatting with
an unfamiliar face.

Original: "You must be the [Guild] Guild.
We were speaking of your hard work
in exploring the small caves.
[Page]
"All of us in this city are grateful
for your contributions. The caves have
many rare and desirable materials.
[Page]
"The more of them you find, the more
we shall flourish. I hope that you
continue your efforts on our behalf.
[Page]
"Ah, have I not introduced myself?
I am Kirtida, owner of the Dancing
Peacock. I'd like it if you visited."
Translation: "You must be the [Guild] Guild.
We were speaking of your hard work
in exploring the small caves.
[Page]
"All of us in this city are grateful
for your contributions. The caves have
many rare and desirable materials.
[Page]
"The more of them you find, the more
we shall flourish. I hope that you
continue your efforts on our behalf.
[Page]
"Ah, have I not introduced myself?
I am Kirtida, owner of the Dancing
Peacock. I'd like it if you visited."

Original: As you enter the inn, you see the
innkeeper in the hall, chatting with
a familiar face.
Translation: As you enter the inn, you see the
innkeeper in the hall, chatting with
a familiar face.

Original: "Ah, it is you. Welcome... I was
speaking with Dalla about your
[Guild] Guild.
[Page]
"It was nothing to be ashamed of...
You seem to be doing your all to search
the small caves that dot these lands.
[Page]
"All of us in this city are grateful
for your contributions. The caves have
many rare and desirable materials.
[Page]
"The more of them you find, the more
we shall flourish. I hope that you
continue your efforts on our behalf.
[Page]
"But now that Dalla has hungry mouths
to feed, I should return to my place
of work. Perhaps later, [Guild]..."
Translation: "Ah, it is you. Welcome... I was
speaking with Dalla about your
[Guild] Guild.
[Page]
"It was nothing to be ashamed of...
You seem to be doing your all to search
the small caves that dot these lands.
[Page]
"All of us in this city are grateful
for your contributions. The caves have
many rare and desirable materials.
[Page]
"The more of them you find, the more
we shall flourish. I hope that you
continue your efforts on our behalf.
[Page]
"But now that Dalla has hungry mouths
to feed, I should return to my place
of work. Perhaps later, [Guild]..."

Original: Upon returning to the inn after a
venture out, you find the guildmaster
munching on a large piece of meat.
Translation: Upon returning to the inn after a
venture out, you find the guildmaster
munching on a large piece of meat.

Original: "Strange running into you here. Why
not try some of that one? No one cooks
finer water buffalo than Dalla.
[Page]
"That reminds me... I heard tell that
you've found quite a few caves
scattered across the Windy Plains.
[Page]
"It's hardly an exaggeration to call
that land the [Guild] Guild's
backyard...
[Page]
"When one chases a single objective,
it can be easy to lose sight of what's
important. Follow your curiosity.
[Page]
"That's the way of a real explorer.
Just keep doing what you're doing,
and things will work out."
Translation: "Strange running into you here. Why
not try some of that one? No one cooks
finer water buffalo than Dalla.
[Page]
"That reminds me... I heard tell that
you've found quite a few caves
scattered across the Windy Plains.
[Page]
"It's hardly an exaggeration to call
that land the [Guild] Guild's
backyard...
[Page]
"When one chases a single objective,
it can be easy to lose sight of what's
important. Follow your curiosity.
[Page]
"That's the way of a real explorer.
Just keep doing what you're doing,
and things will work out."

Original: As you enter the inn to rest your
weary bodies, a knight in armor
passes before you.
[Page]
When your eyes meet, the knight smiles
elegantly and turns to face you.
Translation: As you enter the inn to rest your
weary bodies, a knight in armor
passes before you.
[Page]
When your eyes meet, the knight smiles
elegantly and turns to face you.

Original: "You are Guild [Guild], I assume.
I have heard that you discovered many
dungeons in the Scarlet Pillars.
[Page]
"But excuse my manners. I am Kirjonen,
lowest of the Holy Rune Knights who
serve King Bjornstad.
[Page]
"It is my good fortune to meet such
renowned explorers. I was hoping that
our paths might cross.
[Page]
"If you see a blue-sailed skyship,
that will be mine. Feel free to hail
me in that event. Until then..."
Translation: "You are Guild [Guild], I assume.
I have heard that you discovered many
dungeons in the Scarlet Pillars.
[Page]
"But excuse my manners. I am Kirjonen,
lowest of the Holy Rune Knights who
serve King Bjornstad.
[Page]
"It is my good fortune to meet such
renowned explorers. I was hoping that
our paths might cross.
[Page]
"If you see a blue-sailed skyship,
that will be mine. Feel free to hail
me in that event. Until then..."

Original: As you enter the inn to rest your
weary bodies, a knight in armor
passes before you.
[Page]
When your eyes meet, the knight smiles
elegantly and turns to face you. It is
Kirjonen of the Holy Rune Knights.
Translation: As you enter the inn to rest your
weary bodies, a knight in armor
passes before you.
[Page]
When your eyes meet, the knight smiles
elegantly and turns to face you. It is
Kirjonen of the Holy Rune Knights.

Original: "How do you do, Guild [Guild]?
I've heard of the many labyrinths you
discovered in the Scarlet Pillars.
[Page]
"Each time, it helps me to focus; to
remind me that I still have much to
learn as an explorer.
[Page]
"I hope to someday follow your example
in terms of boldness and vitality.
Perhaps even lend you my strength.
[Page]
"I am glad we could speak in this way.
I have enjoyed this, Guild [Guild].
May we meet next time in the skies."
Translation: "How do you do, Guild [Guild]?
I've heard of the many labyrinths you
discovered in the Scarlet Pillars.
[Page]
"Each time, it helps me to focus; to
remind me that I still have much to
learn as an explorer.
[Page]
"I hope to someday follow your example
in terms of boldness and vitality.
Perhaps even lend you my strength.
[Page]
"I am glad we could speak in this way.
I have enjoyed this, Guild [Guild].
May we meet next time in the skies."

Original: A woman leaving the Saehrimnir Inn
calls out to you.
[Page]
She wears a friendly smile, but you
do not recognize her. Her voice as
she speaks is strong and clear.
Translation: A woman leaving the Saehrimnir Inn
calls out to you.
[Page]
She wears a friendly smile, but you
do not recognize her. Her voice as
she speaks is strong and clear.

Original: "You're... the [Guild] Guild, right?
Are you all done for today?
[Page]
"It's nice to meet you! I'm Wiglaf.
As you can tell, I'm an explorer too.
I've heard so many rumors about you...
[Page]
"Like all the dungeons you found in
the Sacred Mountains. You're really
hard workers, huh?
[Page]
"I gotta get going for today, but I'd
love to hear your stories some other
time! See you around!"
Translation: "You're... the [Guild] Guild, right?
Are you all done for today?
[Page]
"It's nice to meet you! I'm Wiglaf.
As you can tell, I'm an explorer too.
I've heard so many rumors about you...
[Page]
"Like all the dungeons you found in
the Sacred Mountains. You're really
hard workers, huh?
[Page]
"I gotta get going for today, but I'd
love to hear your stories some other
time! See you around!"

belonging to Wiglaf, the explorer
